Map created by myself, Monkey. :)

Do NOT steal, modify, claim to be yours or change the map in any way.

Please comment.

 Tell me if there is a bug with the map and i will fix it asap, it's usually only a quick fix.

Traps included are: Fans, boulders, Explosions, breaking floors, spinning blades on floor, teleporting area which teleports you to a box that slowly kills you, lasers, moving floors, spikes and more.

Sorry about only be able to have up to 20 players i will fix that in my next release (17 CT, 3 T).
